casebody.data:
Chad D. TERRY, Appellant,
v.
STATE of Missouri, Respondent. WD 81423 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. Filed: May 28, 2019 Susan L. Hogan, Kansas City for appellant. Nathan J. Aquino, Jefferson City for respondent. Before Division One: Victor C. Howard, Presiding Judge, Lisa White Hardwick and Gary D. Witt, Judges

ORDER

Per Curiam

Chad Terry appeals from the judgment denying his Rule 29.15 motion following his convictions for first-degree murder and armed criminal action. Upon review of the briefs and the record, we find no error and affirm the post-conviction judgment. We have provided the parties with a Memorandum explaining the reasons for our decision because a published opinion would have no precedential value.

AFFIRMED. Rule 84.16(b).
